### Step 1: Login to get fresh JWT token
POST http://localhost:3000/api/customers/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "sara456",
    "password": "password456"
}

###

### Step 2: Add Item to Cart (Use token from Step 1)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cart/add
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_WITH_TOKEN_FROM_STEP_1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId": "12255",
    "productName": "Automatic Washing Machine",
    "productNameArabic": "غسالة أوتوماتيك",
    "price": 8090,
    "quantity": 1,
    "unit": "نقطة",
    "image": "washing_machine.jpg"
}

###

### Step 3: View Cart
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cart/view
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_WITH_TOKEN_FROM_STEP_1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Step 4: Update Cart Item
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/cart/update
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_WITH_TOKEN_FROM_STEP_1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId": "12255",
    "quantity": 2
}
